#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/5_Hills_of_the_Shorbear_Clan.cfg:378
#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/5_Hills_of_the_Shorbear_Clan.cfg:481
#: data/campaigns/Sceptre_of_Fire/scenarios/5_Hills_of_the_Shorbear_Clan.cfg:541
